Package: CrossClustering
Type: Package
Title: A Partial Clustering Algorithm with Automatic Estimation of the Number of
       Clusters and Identification of Outliers for Spherical or Elongated
       Clusters, with Two Tests for the Significance of the Adjusted Rand Index
       and the Computation of it and Its Confidence Interval from Contingency
       Tables 
Version: 4.0.1
Date: 2018-07-29
