Maintainer: Paola Tellaroli <paola.tellaroli@gmail.com>
Description: This package implements the CrossClustering algorithm, which is a
    partial clustering algorithm that combines the Ward's minimum variance and
    Complete Linkage algorithms, providing automatic estimation of a suitable
    number of clusters and identification of outlier elements.
